[color=#ffff00]How to Play[/color]
Light up all the torches in the room to unlock the door. Some torches are linked and will toggle together when activated. Watch out for bats! Contact with them results in a game over! Your goal is to exit the house through the front yard door.

[color=#ffff00]Controls[/color]
\[Arrows]: Move the character.
\[Space]: Toggle torches.

Press [color=#ffff00]Space[/color] to start...
[color=#ffff00]Golden key[/color] is required to unlock this door.
